[32m+[m[32m| **F4** | `napi-rs` bindings for Rust SIMD combo scorer + regex prefilter | core + tokn | L | ☐ Q4 2026 |[m
[32m+[m[32m| **F5** | `napi-rs` bindings for Rust semantic cache + reasoning replay | core + tokn | L | ☐ Q4 2026 |[m
[32m+[m[32m| **F6** | `cgo` integration for in-process Bifrost Go SDK (Bifrost's v1.0 GA gate) | core | M | ☐ 2027 Q1 |[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m#### 2.5.7 Per-edge binding map (baseline 2026-07-04)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m| Edge | Recommended tier | Driver |[m
[32m+[m[32m|---|---|---|[m
