[32m+[m[32m## 17. Polyglot Binding Tiers (ADR-032)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m> **Added 2026-07-04 (L5-114).** See [`docs/adr/0032-polyglot-binding-tiers.md`](adr/0032-polyglot-binding-tiers.md)[m
[32m+[m[32m> for the full MADR.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mOmniRoute's Tier-2 engine (TypeScript) talks to non-TS substrates — Bifrost[m
[32m+[m[32m(Go), Tokn (Rust), phenotype-routing (Rust), `dispatch-mcp` (Go) — over[m
[32m+[m[32m**three binding tiers**, picked per-edge:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m| Tier | Mechanism | Overhead | Hot-path fit |[m
[32m+[m[32m|---|---|---|---|[m
[32m+[m[32m| **T1 — HTTP sidecar** (default) | `fetch()` over TCP loopback | ~1-2 ms | Tier-1 router (`BifrostBackendExecutor.execute`), dashboards, ops endpoints |[m
[32m+[m[32m| **T2 — Unix-domain-socket (UDS) RPC** | JSON-RPC / Cap'n Proto / FlatBuffers over UDS | ~50-200 µs | High-RPS Tier-2 modules (compression, translator, MCP client) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| **T3 — Native ABI FFI** | `napi-rs` (Node↔Rust), `cgo` (Node↔Go), `pyo3` (Python↔Rust) | ~1-10 µs | Inner loops (SSE chunking, combo scoring, tokenization, regex prefilter) |[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Default tier per edge:**[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m| Edge | Tier | Source file |[m
[32m+[m[32m|---|---|---|[m
[32m+[m[32m| Tier-1 router dispatch (TS ↔ Go) | T1 (keep) | `open-sse/executors/bifrost.ts:107-244` |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Format translation (OpenAI↔Anthropic↔Gemini) | T3 (FFI via `napi-rs`) | `open-sse/translator/` (planned F4) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Prompt compression (lite/caveman/rtk) | T2 → T3 at 1k RPS | `open-sse/services/compression/` (planned F3) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Combo scorer (12-factor Auto-Combo) | T3 (FFI → Rust SIMD) | `open-sse/services/autoCombo/scoring.ts` (planned F4) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| SSE chunking | T3 (FFI → Rust `futures::stream`) | `open-sse/handlers/chatCore.ts:1042-1058` (planned F4) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Rate-limit token-bucket (DEBT-001) | T3 (FFI → Rust `parking_lot`) | `open-sse/services/rateLimitManager.ts` (planned F5) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Semantic cache + reasoning replay | T3 (FFI → Rust `dashmap`) | `open-sse/services/reasoningCache.ts` (planned F5) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Guardrail hot path (PII, prompt-injection) | T2 (UDS RPC → Rust `regex`/`aho-corasick`) | `src/lib/guardrails/` (planned F3) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| MCP server tool dispatch (co-located) | T2 (UDS RPC) | `open-sse/mcp-server/` (planned F3) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Pricing sync, dashboard rollups, webhooks | T1 (keep) | `src/lib/pricingSync.ts`, `src/lib/webhookDispatcher.ts` |[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Why T1 by default?** Backwards compatibility, kill-switch semantics[m
[32m+[m[32minherited from `open-sse/services/bifrostKillSwitch.ts:382-416`, and zero[m
[32m+[m[32mnew ops surface.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Why T3 for the inner loops?** Zero-copy buffers (`napi-rs` `Buffer` is a[m
[32m+[m[32mdirect view into the Rust `Vec<u8>`), sub-10µs overhead, and lock-free[m
[32m+[m[32mprimitives (`parking_lot`, `dashmap`, `crossbeam`) are not achievable over[m
[32m+[m[32mIPC.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Rollout** (see `PLAN.md` § 2.5.6 for full F1-F6 table):[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **F1**: pick canonical UDS RPC framework (Q3 2026, S)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **F2**: `crates/tokn` extraction + UDS RPC server (Q3 2026, M)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **F3**: migrate compression + guardrails to UDS RPC (Q3 2026, M)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **F4**: `napi-rs` SIMD combo scorer + SSE chunking (Q4 2026, L)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **F5**: `napi-rs` semantic cache + reasoning replay (Q4 2026, L)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **F6**: `cgo` in-process Bifrost Go SDK (2027 Q1, M)[m
